name: BET 004
description:
Each bag is unique, handcrafted and embroidered with love and care with the best quality materials.

Items can be made to order, please allow a little extra time for delivery. 
Do not hesitate to contact us if you want to place an order or be informed when new similar products come out.

SIZES 30cm x 24 cm // 11 cm

MATERIAL Outer: Leather, basket and cotton / Lining: 70% cotton, 30% silk

DESCRIPTION  Backpack handbag with basketry base.
Flap embroidered with a face with ropes and varied applications.
Leather handles with cotton lining and golden hardware and buckles of the best quality.
Magnet closure with decorative buckle.
Interior zippered bag with lining with interior pocket.
